dc_title_s: Census Designated Places (500k Carto Boundary File), WI 2000
dc_description_s: This data represents Census Designated Places from the U.S. Census Bureau for Wisconsin in 2000. [The 2000 cartographic boundary shapefiles are simplified representations of selected geographic areas from the Census Bureau's MAF/TIGER geographic database. These boundary files are specifically designed for small scale thematic mapping.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
